entries.femaleVariant: Get everything you need?
Yep, that'll do. Thanks, Judy.
So, what now?
Speakin' of harm's way. Know what I see lookin' at you?
So, what now?
Walking, talking corpses.
We really needed that recording, Judy.
Relax – everything's under control.
We needed that recording, Judy. BD practically does our job for us.
entries.maleVariant: We needed that recording, Judy. The BD practically does our job for us.

entries.femaleVariant: Relax, I got it all under control.
If Arasaka finds out you have it, you're dead. I'M dead.
If you fuck up and they come knockin' on my door...
Evelyn, please... no shortcuts.
Connection to Yorinobu – what's its nature, exactly?
Think I see how you know so much about Yorinobu.
We got it. Later, T-Bug.
Nice work today. See ya soon.
Biz. And biz only.
Thanks for the help.
Till next time. I hope.
Thanks, Judy. Really.
And don't worry – I know what I'm doin'.
Well, don't worry. Won't do anything to get you in trouble. But, uh... I hope to see you again?
Depends.
On what?
Whether you come alone or with a tag-along. Like a netrunner.
No 'runners. I promise.
See ya.
Keep it. I'll put it on Ev's tab.
Portable device for handling BDs. I already uploaded your calibration settings.
And it keeps you outta harm's way. Clever.
'Course I will be.
[Stand]
Not as sophisticated as what we got here, but should do the trick.
Judy... relax. That's not gonna happen.
Judy... relax. Nobody will ever know.
It's simple – men like pillow talk a bit too much.
So it's just about the sex?
I'll wipe the cache and your data. You were never here.
Do this job for me. I mean me alone. No splitting the payout with anyone else. No middlemen.
No Dex.
I'll think about it.
No way. Dex trusts me.
You wanna haze our fixer?
If I agree, there'll be hell to pay. For sure.
No fuckin' way. Dex took a leap with me. He trusts me.
You wanna fuck over our fixer. I knew something was up.
I know. Whatever you decide, it stays between us.
I can offer fifty percent. Eddies enough to do whatever the hell you like.
I'll be finished. Dex won't forgive a dirt move like this.
Dex isn't the only fixer in town. But my offer's the only one you'll ever get.
Huh, lemme think about it.
Now I'm doing the same. Fifty percent. With cred like that in your account, you won't need Dex for anything.
I'm not about to fuck Dex over.
I'll think about it.
No, Evelyn. It's not just about the money.
I thought you were a merc. I thought it was always about the money.
Not behind the back of someone who trusts me. Sorry.
Fine. I never asked. But V?
Hmm?
I just hope you're as good as you are naive.
I'll think about it.
Dex is a middleman. And a useless one, at this point.
Your choice.
You sure you wanna do this?
But if we're smart...
If you need me, call. I'll send you my number.
OK.
Good luck.
Mmhm.
Evelyn, you don't mess with fixers. That's the one rule every merc in this city knows – and actually follows.
Doesn't matter. Mistake like that'll cost you your rep. And without a rep, you're nobody.
You sure everything's under control?
Intel on Yorinobu, the chip, the BD from Konpeki... Winds are right, plan's perfect. A job like this comes one in a million.
Mm. Thanks. Now the punch line, please.
Just sounds too good to be true. What's the catch?
I wanna know if you're really in control here. That you're not sending me into the sorta shit I can't wade out of.
Cold feet? Are you looking to get out of it?
V. I have zero reasons to haze you. We're in this together. Really. Trust me that I got this.
You're sure Yorinobu doesn't expect this kinda move from you?
He's got no idea, trust me. He's too busy with NetWatch to give me that kind of attention.
Besides... even IF some suspicion takes root in his mind, it shouldn't matter, he won't react in time. And that's something you'll handle, right?
You're not worried? Arasaka will flag and screen anyone who's had dealings with Yorinobu.
They'll have a long list, then. Packed full of big names. Much bigger than mine.
You tell me who they check first. Corpo hotshots and cutthroats? Or a little bedroom plaything like me?
Not afraid they'll tie you to the heist?
You sure Yorinobu doesn't suspect a thing?
Now go. I need a few words with Judy.
See you, V.
Time's a-wastin', V.
Besides, we'll talk in a bit.
V, one sec.
Let's walk.
The BD will be the death of us. Seriously.
You go that route, city'll always win. So be careful.
Better ask yourself that question. Do you want to spend the rest of your days blasting scavs? Or become a legend overnight?
